                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">读到后来会有些许麻木，人的一生像条河流，而人和人之间像密布交叉的河网。这些人.事.行当都慢慢消失了</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1031121527">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1031121527" class="vote-count">4</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1031121527" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1031121527">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Shhhhhhhh/">♣Faith.</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2016-04-12</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">虽然形式大于内容，但至少申赋渔×朱嬴椿这对坑钱好搭档，让不少人在纸书沦为非主流的时代遇到真爱了</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

<div id="comments" class="comment-list new noshow">
